---
description: Django events backend assignment guardrails
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: true
---

Read SPEC.md and AGENTS.md before doing any work.

Never:
- swap Django's User model
- add username to signup request
- allow unverified login
- skip role checks
- skip ownership checks
- skip tests
- change API behavior without updating README/Postman

Always:
- plan first
- list files to edit before editing
- implement one phase at a time
- run migrations, tests, and lint after each phase
- verify pagination and error envelope against SPEC.md
